{"tid":641752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple rip?庫克周四凌晨晤特朗普　料談及中美貿易問題","createTime":"2018-04-25T08:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T13:27:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1415db62f73941e7eb6a6a965789da302530b85e","tid":641752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，美國白宮正式公布，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)行政總裁庫克將於香港時間周四(4月26日)凌晨1時45分，在美國華盛頓會見美國總統特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n白宮沒有提及雙方討論的話題，但美國媒體估計，雙方正值中美貿易衝突敏應時刻會面，料會談及相關的科技議題，例如美國近期就對中興通訊採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180425/bkn-20180425152801897-0425_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180425%2Fbkn-20180425152801897-0425_00842_001.html&d=S8c6LNgzw8aMKwOJUYsK6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=5f499f8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180425/bkn-20180425152801897-0425_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a30ef0668a97327de13ff553d2d06c974b67ba91","tid":641752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"a32201a842ee487c3dca2b1ba3ef3999886b93c1","tid":641752,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"逼佢將iCLOUD搬出支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e537679d3d8e64b5e6a35ac89f9d2fd4989f10","tid":641752,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"Trump : No more sale in支那！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/lz9umlhvzvqlappqptyt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Flz9umlhvzvqlappqptyt.jpg&h=ed6f5386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643ea33683cbd12f73